I had nothing to do with it.

410
00:54:47,577 --> 00:54:49,204
Your husband's crazy.

411
00:54:49,454 --> 00:54:54,250
What kind of relationship
did you have with Lt. Cadet?

412
00:54:57,086 --> 00:55:02,342
I'm a widow. My business
and that of Lt. Cadet...

413
00:55:02,467 --> 00:55:04,677
are no concern of the law.

414
00:55:06,679 --> 00:55:10,350
All right.
Did you know that,

415
00:55:10,725 --> 00:55:14,354
as a result of these affairs,
Lt. Cadet was transferred to Albania?

416
00:55:14,479 --> 00:55:15,522
