417
00:55:15,563 --> 00:55:19,067
And before his departure,
he was questioned in judicial inquiry.

418
00:55:19,359 --> 00:55:20,443
Clerk.

419
00:55:20,485 --> 00:55:22,946
He declared to have encountered

420
00:55:23,071 --> 00:55:27,492
the widow Scordia only twice...
in her home,

421
00:55:27,492 --> 00:55:31,955
and to have had
no amorous relationship...

422
00:55:32,080 --> 00:55:36,459
considering their relationship
"just a casual friendship."

423
00:55:40,255 --> 00:55:41,464
Son of a bitch.

