certain feelings.

427
00:55:53,142 --> 00:55:56,646
But unlike the married Cusimano,

428
00:55:57,021 --> 00:56:01,776
who was, let's face it, guilty...

429
00:56:01,985 --> 00:56:04,654
of senile dimming of the senses...

430
00:56:05,405 --> 00:56:07,657
of an intoxicating
kaleidoscope of desires...

431
00:56:07,740 --> 00:56:13,288
Unlike the family man Cusimano...

432
00:56:13,371 --> 00:56:15,498
Cadet is...

433
00:56:15,748 --> 00:56:19,752
and was...

434
00:56:20,003 --> 00:56:21,170
a bachelor... a bachelor!

435
00:56:21,379 --> 00:56:23,381
Clever, that lawyer.

436
00:56:23,882 --> 00:56:25,425
