437
00:56:25,925 --> 00:56:30,763
Careful investigation
of the facts tell us, therefore...

438
00:56:31,055 --> 00:56:34,183
that the Scordia woman
committed no other crime...

439
00:56:34,309 --> 00:56:36,936
than that of being ill-fated,

440
00:56:37,186 --> 00:56:40,815
alone and beautiful.

441
00:56:41,190 --> 00:56:43,067
Here is her crime - her beauty!

442
00:56:43,192 --> 00:56:44,736
And from here, the envy,

443
00:56:44,777 --> 00:56:47,322
the lies, the disgrace,

444
00:56:47,780 --> 00:56:50,867
that have deprived her
even of a father's trust!

445
00:56:50,909 --> 00:56:55,538
And yet, she herself
is still in silent agony...

446
00:56:56,372 --> 00:56:59,417
mourning over
that unmarked war grave...

447
00:57:00,335 --> 00:57:05,715
in faraway East Africa.

448
00:57:06,799 --> 00:57:10,178
In the beating heart of our argument...

449
00:57:10,303 --> 00:57:14,933
