in the shelter of a new life?

454
00:57:29,614 --> 00:57:32,992
Does she have the right
to yearn for, and to write...

455
00:57:33,201 --> 00:57:36,245
a new ending to her own love story?

456
00:57:37,080 --> 00:57:39,082
Your Honor,

457
00:57:39,248 --> 00:57:41,459
the citizens of Castelcuto reply:
"Yes!"

458
00:57:52,887 --> 00:57:55,139
