You'll never have to worry again.

477
00:59:28,983 --> 00:59:33,488
I forgive her. She did it
to pay her lawyer's fees

478
00:59:33,571 --> 00:59:35,114
only once and never again.

479
00:59:35,239 --> 00:59:37,492
